{
  "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
  "voice": "zh-CN-YunxiNeural",
  "voice_key": "yunxi",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "一个方波，棱角分明，上下笔直地跳变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.58,
      "size": 25344,
      "text": "我们能否用光滑的正弦波，一层层把它拼出来？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "傅里叶说可以，只要把足够多的正弦叠加起来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "partial",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "partial-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/partial-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.68,
      "size": 42912,
      "text": "方波的傅里叶级数只含奇次谐波：sin x、sin 3x、sin 5x……"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "partial",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "partial-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/partial-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "取前 n 项相加，就得到部分和，它像波浪一样贴近方波。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "partial",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "partial-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/partial-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "项数越多，平坦段越平，逼近看起来越来越好。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "overshoot",
      "line_id": "ovs-1",
      "filename": "overshoot-ovs-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/overshoot-ovs-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "可是盯住跳变点，你会发现曲线总是冲过了头。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "overshoot",
      "line_id": "ovs-2",
      "filename": "overshoot-ovs-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/overshoot-ovs-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "紧挨跳变的地方，鼓起一个小尖角，然后来回振铃。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "gibbs",
      "line_id": "gib-1",
      "filename": "gibbs-gib-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/gibbs-gib-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "奇妙的是，这个过冲约等于跳变量的百分之九。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "gibbs",
      "line_id": "gib-2",
      "filename": "gibbs-gib-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/gibbs-gib-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.17,
      "size": 34704,
      "text": "无论加到五十项还是五千项，它都顽固地停在九个百分点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "再盯着跳变点的红色尖峰，它却始终高高地立在那儿。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "部分和整体收敛，跳变点却留下固定的过冲。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "这提醒我们：逐点逼近和一致逼近，并不是一回事。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "gibbs-phenomenon",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/gibbs-phenomenon/yunxi/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "一道跳变，藏着九个百分点的秘密，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 27.099999999999998,
  "total_size": 433872
}